<plot>A mother sets down her child in the backyard, and then goes back into the house for a brief moment. But as soon as she is gone, the child crawls inside the doghouse. When the mother comes back outside, she does not see where the child has gone, and she frantically begins to look for him. Soon she has the whole neighborhood in turmoil.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?572399</url></doc>
